{"title":"Hexo+Aurora为什么是神","uid":"b95dc70bfc2b7fc64705eefbea672b7e","slug":"Aurora为什么是神","date":"2022-02-09T05:18:13.000Z","updated":"2022-02-10T06:14:02.037Z","comments":true,"path":"api/articles/Aurora为什么是神.json","keywords":null,"cover":"https://img.wenhairu.com/images/2022/02/09/QpQ7A.png","content":"<h1 id=\"本文\"><a href=\"#本文\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"本文\"></a>本文</h1><ul>\n<li>将会向你介绍Hexo，Aurora为什么是<strong>神</strong></li>\n<li>将会告诉你如何搭建本地Hexo+Aurora服务器</li>\n<li>不会告诉你如何将hexo部署到Github Pages，因为这已经烂大街了</li>\n<li><del>是处女作</del></li>\n</ul>\n<h1 id=\"Hexo简介\"><a href=\"#Hexo简介\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"Hexo简介\"></a>Hexo简介</h1><p>这是一款<strong>快速、简洁且高效</strong>的博客框架<br>详情请见<a href=\"https://hexo.io/zh-cn/\">Hexo</a></p>\n<h1 id=\"Aurora简介\"><a href=\"#Aurora简介\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"Aurora简介\"></a>Aurora简介</h1><p>这是Hexo的一个<strong>主题</strong></p>\n<h2 id=\"优点\"><a href=\"#优点\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"优点\"></a>优点</h2><ul>\n<li><p>优雅 UI</p>\n<ul>\n<li>主题的主要设计理念是基于当下流行的 “极光UI”。</li>\n<li><em><strong>没错人家就是好看～～～</strong></em></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li><p>Vue3 驱动</p>\n<ul>\n<li>享受由 Vue3 建立的单页面应用（SPA）所带来的更优雅，更友好的用户体验。</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li><p>高性能</p>\n<ul>\n<li>使用 Vue3 给整个博客主题带来了整体的性能提升。</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li><p>高度自定义</p>\n<ul>\n<li>config文件完善，完善的插件适配，自定义色彩，自定义菜单，语法简洁</li>\n<li>详情见<a href=\"https://aurora.tridiamond.tech/zh/\">Hexo Aurora</a></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<h1 id=\"Hexo安装\"><a href=\"#Hexo安装\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"Hexo安装\"></a>Hexo安装</h1>  <pre class=\"line-numbers language-Bash\" data-language=\"Bash\"><code class=\"language-Bash\">npm install hexo-cli -g<span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"line-numbers-rows\"><span></span></span></code></pre>\n\n<h1 id=\"成神之路-For-MacOS\"><a href=\"#成神之路-For-MacOS\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"成神之路(For MacOS)\"></a>成神之路(For MacOS)</h1><h2 id=\"前置\"><a href=\"#前置\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"前置\"></a>前置</h2><ul>\n<li>brew（用来安装npm hhh)，不会有人没安装brew吧？<br> 安装brew <pre class=\"line-numbers language-Bash\" data-language=\"Bash\"><code class=\"language-Bash\">&#x2F;bin&#x2F;bash -c &quot;$(curl -fsSL https:&#x2F;&#x2F;raw.githubusercontent.com&#x2F;Homebrew&#x2F;install&#x2F;HEAD&#x2F;install.sh)&quot;<span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"line-numbers-rows\"><span></span></span></code></pre></li>\n<li>npm&#x2F;yarn(推荐使用npm，因为我用的npm)<br> 安装npm <pre class=\"line-numbers language-Bash\" data-language=\"Bash\"><code class=\"language-Bash\">brew install npm<span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"line-numbers-rows\"><span></span></span></code></pre></li>\n<li>hexo &gt;&#x3D; 5.0 <del>(我猜的)</del><br> <a href=\"#hexo%E5%AE%89%E8%A3%85\">安装hexo</a></li>\n</ul>\n<h2 id=\"开始\"><a href=\"#开始\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"开始\"></a>开始</h2><h3 id=\"建站\"><a href=\"#建站\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"建站\"></a>建站</h3><pre class=\"line-numbers language-Bash\" data-language=\"Bash\"><code class=\"language-Bash\">cd &#123;the_folder_you_want&#125;\nhexo init &#123;blog_name_you_want&#125;<span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"line-numbers-rows\"><span></span><span></span></span></code></pre>\n<h3 id=\"安装Aurora\"><a href=\"#安装Aurora\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"安装Aurora\"></a>安装Aurora</h3><p>在<code>&#123;blog_name_you_want&#125;</code>文件夹内执行</p>\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-Bash\" data-language=\"Bash\"><code class=\"language-Bash\">npm install hexo-theme-aurora --save<span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"line-numbers-rows\"><span></span></span></code></pre>\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-bash\" data-language=\"bash\"><code class=\"language-bash\"><span class=\"token function\">cp</span> -rf ./node_modules/hexo-theme-aurora/_config.yml ./_config.aurora.yml<span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"line-numbers-rows\"><span></span></span></code></pre>\n<p>这样，就可以编辑aurora的配置文件了</p>\n<div class=\"custom-quote tip\">\n<span class=\"custom-quote-svg\"><svg width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" data-reactroot=\"\">\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M20.86 14.13C20 14.7 19.56 15.74 19.77 16.76C20.13 18.55 18.55 20.13 16.76 19.77C15.74 19.57 14.7 20 14.13 20.86C13.12 22.38 10.89 22.38 9.88 20.86C9.3 20 8.26 19.56 7.24 19.77C5.45 20.13 3.87 18.55 4.23 16.76C4.43 15.74 4 14.7 3.14 14.13C1.62 13.12 1.62 10.89 3.14 9.88C4 9.3 4.44 8.26 4.23 7.24C3.87 5.45 5.45 3.87 7.24 4.23C8.26 4.44 9.3 4 9.87 3.14C10.88 1.62 13.11 1.62 14.12 3.14C14.7 4 15.74 4.44 16.76 4.23C18.55 3.87 20.13 5.45 19.77 7.24C19.56 8.26 20 9.3 20.86 9.87C22.38 10.88 22.38 13.12 20.86 14.13Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M12.01 15C12.01 14.5 12.01 14.5 12.01 14.5C12.04 13.75 13 13.46 14.04 12.2C14.41 11.74 14.69 11.41 14.86 10.85C15.15 9.95 14.92 9.18 14.86 9.02C14.8 8.79 14.52 8 13.72 7.46C13.06 7.02 12.42 7 12.14 7C11.9 7 11.36 7 10.78 7.3C10.28 7.56 9.98 7.9 9.83 8.1C9.24 8.82 9.06 9.63 9 10.06\"></path>\n<path stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M11.99 18H12.01\"></path>\n</svg></span>\n<p class=\"custom-quote-title\">TIP</p>\n<p>注意，不能直接更改<code>./node_modules/hexo-theme-aurora/_config.yml</code>！会出问题！</p>\n</div>\n<h3 id=\"启用Aurora\"><a href=\"#启用Aurora\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"启用Aurora\"></a>启用Aurora</h3><p>在在<code>&#123;blog_name_you_want&#125;</code>文件夹内找到<code>_config.yml</code>，修改其中<code>theme</code>字段，如下：</p>\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-YML\" data-language=\"YML\"><code class=\"language-YML\"># Extensions\n## Plugins: https:&#x2F;&#x2F;hexo.io&#x2F;plugins&#x2F;\n## Themes: https:&#x2F;&#x2F;hexo.io&#x2F;themes&#x2F;\ntheme: aurora<span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"line-numbers-rows\"><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span></span></code></pre>\n<h3 id=\"生成静态网页，启动网站\"><a href=\"#生成静态网页，启动网站\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"生成静态网页，启动网站\"></a>生成静态网页，启动网站</h3><p>最后，只需要</p>\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-Bash\" data-language=\"Bash\"><code class=\"language-Bash\">hexo g &amp;&amp; hexo s<span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"line-numbers-rows\"><span></span></span></code></pre>\n<div class=\"custom-quote tip\">\n<span class=\"custom-quote-svg\"><svg width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" data-reactroot=\"\">\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M20.86 14.13C20 14.7 19.56 15.74 19.77 16.76C20.13 18.55 18.55 20.13 16.76 19.77C15.74 19.57 14.7 20 14.13 20.86C13.12 22.38 10.89 22.38 9.88 20.86C9.3 20 8.26 19.56 7.24 19.77C5.45 20.13 3.87 18.55 4.23 16.76C4.43 15.74 4 14.7 3.14 14.13C1.62 13.12 1.62 10.89 3.14 9.88C4 9.3 4.44 8.26 4.23 7.24C3.87 5.45 5.45 3.87 7.24 4.23C8.26 4.44 9.3 4 9.87 3.14C10.88 1.62 13.11 1.62 14.12 3.14C14.7 4 15.74 4.44 16.76 4.23C18.55 3.87 20.13 5.45 19.77 7.24C19.56 8.26 20 9.3 20.86 9.87C22.38 10.88 22.38 13.12 20.86 14.13Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M12.01 15C12.01 14.5 12.01 14.5 12.01 14.5C12.04 13.75 13 13.46 14.04 12.2C14.41 11.74 14.69 11.41 14.86 10.85C15.15 9.95 14.92 9.18 14.86 9.02C14.8 8.79 14.52 8 13.72 7.46C13.06 7.02 12.42 7 12.14 7C11.9 7 11.36 7 10.78 7.3C10.28 7.56 9.98 7.9 9.83 8.1C9.24 8.82 9.06 9.63 9 10.06\"></path>\n<path stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M11.99 18H12.01\"></path>\n</svg></span>\n<p class=\"custom-quote-title\">TIP</p>\n<p>如果之前生成过其他主题的网页，建议在这之前先执行</p>\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-Bash\" data-language=\"Bash\"><code class=\"language-Bash\">hexo clean<span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"line-numbers-rows\"><span></span></span></code></pre>\n</p>\n</div>\n<p>正常输出应该如下所示：</p>\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-Log\" data-language=\"Log\"><code class=\"language-Log\">INFO  Validating config\nINFO  Start processing\nINFO API data generated by Aurora v1.5.5\nINFO  Hexo is running at http:&#x2F;&#x2F;localhost:4000&#x2F; . Press Ctrl+C to stop.\nINFO Thanks for 